</body>
 films such as <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../229/1470229.xml">
Splash</link></it> and <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../852/1472852.xml">
Down and Out in Beverly Hills</link></it> for Target and their <link>
Star Books</link> imprint. Some of these books were published under the pen name 'Ian Don'.</p>
<p>

